TO ANYTHING I SAY.

13:11.650 --> 13:13.163
- FOR WHAT REASON?
- BECAUSE YOU'RE IN HIGH SCHOOL,

13:13.270 --> 13:14.578
AND YOU'RE NOT STAYING HERE
BY YOURSELF.

13:14.690 --> 13:16.442
- YEAH, BUT WHEN AMBER WAS 17,
WE USED TO STAY ALONE.

13:16.550 --> 13:18.859
- WELL, I'VE LEARNED
A FEW THINGS SINCE THEN.

13:18.970 --> 13:21.200
- YEAH, AMBER'S CRAZY,
AND I'M NOT.

13:21.310 --> 13:22.868
- I KNOW
YOU'RE NOT CRAZY, HONEY.

13:22.970 --> 13:24.039
- DOES THIS MAKE ANY SENSE?

13:24.140 --> 13:25.619
PLEASE.
- YEAH. YEAH.

13:25.730 --> 13:28.107
NO, UM,
IT'S ALREADY SET UP

13:28.220 --> 13:30.074
TO GO TO YOUR GRAN DPARENTS'
HOUSE, SO...

13:30.180 --> 13:34.116
- [scoffs]
ALL RIGHT, FINE.

13:34.220 --> 13:37.041
[door closes]
- [sighs]

