AND MAYBE YOU'LL FIND OUT--

14:15.950 --> 14:18.089
- I'M SORRY, HANK,
THIS HAS TO BE THIS WEEKEND?

14:18.200 --> 14:19.121
- YEAH, I-I--
YEAH.

14:19.230 --> 14:21.505
- BUT I-I TOO OFF
THIS WEEKEND.

14:21.610 --> 14:23.191
I'M--I TOOK OFF
ON FRIDAY AND SATURDAY.

14:23.310 --> 14:24.789
I'M GOING TO THAT WEDDING
IN NAPA.

14:24.890 --> 14:26.266
- OH.
OH, THAT'S THIS WEEKEND?

14:26.380 --> 14:29.850
- YEAH.

14:29.970 --> 14:31.653
