FOR THIS WEEKEND?

14:31.760 --> 14:33.625
- YEAH, YEAH, YEAH.
BUT OKAY.

14:33.730 --> 14:35.766
ALL RIGHT, YOU GOT PLANS?

14:35.870 --> 14:38.247
- IT WAS--IT'S IN THE BOOK.

14:38.360 --> 14:40.419
- YEAH, YEAH,
I GOT TO GET DOWN THERE,

14:40.530 --> 14:42.589
