14:56.170 --> 14:57.819
- YEAH, OKAY. YEAH.

14:57.930 --> 14:59.682
- LET ME TALK ABOUT IT
WITH MARK.

14:59.790 --> 15:01.519
MAYBE WE CAN FIGURE
SOMETHING OUT.

15:01.620 --> 15:02.928
- APPRECIATE IT.
- YEAH.

15:03.040 --> 15:06.032
- WELL, NOW,
I CAN SEE THAT THERE'S

15:06.140 --> 15:08.199
