17:49.300 --> 17:50.710
- CAN I HAVE ONE OF THOSE HATS
WITH THE LIGHT ON IT?

17:50.820 --> 17:52.924
- UH, YES, AND SOON.
YEAH.

17:53.030 --> 17:54.201
- WOW.
- YEAH.

17:54.310 --> 17:55.584
- THIS IS--
